# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback.
#
# The React app is a single page application; client side routing
# handles every visible path. Without this rule, a hard refresh on a
# non root path (e.g., /heatmap) returns 404 from Cloudflare's edge
# because the file does not exist. Rewriting every unmatched path to
# /index.html (status 200) hands the URL to the SPA router.
#
# Reference: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/platform/redirects/

/*    /index.html    200
